<br>
You want Named Drakes FFA?  Fine.  I'll be there with 20-30 NB EVERY patch.  We NEED Named drake to finsh quests, not Doze.  You think you can beat NB, TL and BotS to Named?  We all need them to complete our quests.  Every patch we will be there, killing all the armor giving mobs, because yea I have some twinks that could use armor.  BotS will be 3 screens away camping 2 other Named, and Tindi will be in another spot camping those named.  Every 7 days, every patch.  This is what will happen if Named Drake go FFA.  You think you'll get alot of armor farming in while we're there?<br>
<br>
Or... Doze and Named are treated as one rotation like they are now.  The guild thats up for Doze comes in once a week, for 2-3 hours and then is gone, and you can farm armor all the rest of the time.<br>
<br>
You think we wouldn't love for named drake to be FFA?  We complete 1 Doze quest every 1-2 months now.  If named drakes were FFA we would be there everytime they spawned, making sure we were there before you to kill them.  We could probably complete 3-4 quests in the first month alone.<br>
<br>
But thats not what rotations are about.  Rotations are here to fairly share the resources of the server between all that can kill them. <p><P><A HREF="http://www.jakefitch.com/asb/char_detail.asp?Name=Milambus" TARGET="_blank"><IMG SRC="http://jakefitch.com/sig/eq/sig1.jpg" HEIGHT="150" WIDTH="400" ALT="Milambus Mandragon" BORDER="0"></A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#222222><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/umilambus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Milambus</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_redspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>RTA Admin</span><br>  Posts: 822<br> <font color=#00FFFF>(9/16/02 7:03:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm50.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=121.topic&index=66>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://jakefitch.com/sig/eq/profile/fist1.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: A few months ago...</span><hr size=1> Jurrasic to answer the question: <br>
<br>
Rotations rules/etc are created via discussion.  If all the Doze guilds got together and after discusion agreed to make the named FFA then thats what would happen.  Its not just a simple vote for each rule.  Rotations are package deals that are compromises that the guild on the rotation make.<br>
<br>
So can the rule be changed?  Sure.  Can you convince the other guilds that such a change is best?  Maybe.<br>
<br>
Glyhed/Exiled is a new rotation that took alot of discussing to get the exact details worked out.  All 3 guilds gave thier input until an agreement was made that all could live with. <p><P><A HREF="http://www.jakefitch.com/asb/char_detail.asp?Name=Milambus" TARGET="_blank"><IMG SRC="http://jakefitch.com/sig/eq/sig1.jpg" HEIGHT="150" WIDTH="400" ALT="Milambus Mandragon" BORDER="0"></A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ujurrasicepoch.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jurrasic Epoch</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_magentaspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>FK Rep</span><br>  Posts: 476<br> <font color=#00FFFF>(9/16/02 7:09:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm50.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=121.topic&index=67>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://thegeekhost.com/gravedirt/friend.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: A few months ago...</span><hr size=1> Thank you, that is what I was looking for, and I was asking for clarification for the future regarding mobs that I imagine will be linked via planar advancement quests in PoP that some guilds will have access to before others, but circumstances may be different then with doze/named.<br>
